These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
7 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, guinea-pig, goat, hedgehog, mouse, pony
 1. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 2. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the hedgehog##7
 3. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the horse##7
 4. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 5. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8
 6. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 8. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the pony##7
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
10. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Pet   | hedgehog | horse | rabbit | guinea-pig | goat | mouse | pony |

