.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
There 7 different types of food: radish, plum, pepper, cranberry, lemon, asparagus, carrot
 1. the person eating asparagus is the person eating asparagus##1
 2. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5
 3. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
 4. the person eating plum is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 6. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
 7. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 9. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
10. the person eating lemon is not to the left of the person eating radish##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Food   | cranberry | plum | asparagus | carrot | pepper | radish | lemon |

