 5. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person playing poker##7
 6. the person playing poker is somewhere between the person playing go and the person playing whist##7
 7. the person playing go is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
 8. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 9. the person playing whist is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
10. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Game   | bridge | go | poker | whist | domino | chess | billiard |

