4. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
6. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person who likes amber##7
8. the person who likes apricot is somewhere between the person who likes pink and the person who likes white##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Color   | ebony | amber | fuchsia | pink | apricot | white | blood-red |

