 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 7. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
 8. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 9. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is soccer##2
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
