 6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 7. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 8. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of country is not to the right of the fan of jazz##8
10. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
11. the fan of r&b is not to the right of the fan of punk##8
12. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
13. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5
